  "notes": "<h2 style=\"letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><b>✨ Team — Today’s Game Plan ✨</b></h2><p style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"></p><p class=\"p2\" style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><br></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span class=\"s1\"></span></p><h3 style=\"letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><b>🧼 Stockroom</b></h3><p style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span class=\"s1\"></span></p><ul style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><li><p class=\"p1\">🗂️ Keep COG racks clean &amp; organized</p></li><li><p class=\"p1\">📦 Restock&nbsp;<span class=\"s1\"><b>tuxedo shirts</b></span>&nbsp;first</p></li><li><p class=\"p1\">😴 Move&nbsp;<span class=\"s1\"><b>slow linen shirts</b></span>&nbsp;back to Moda</p></li></ul><p style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"></p><p class=\"p2\" style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><br></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span class=\"s1\"></span></p><h3 style=\"letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><b>📊 Inventory</b></h3><p style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span class=\"s1\"></span></p><ul style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><li><p class=\"p1\">🔍 Complete&nbsp;<span class=\"s1\"><b>daily scan</b></span>&nbsp;by midday</p></li><li><p class=\"p1\">🎯 Keep accuracy&nbsp;<span class=\"s1\"><b>on target</b><b></b></span></p></li><li><p class=\"p1\">🚫 Report any mismatches immediately</p></li></ul><p style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"></p><p class=\"p2\" style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><br></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span class=\"s1\"></span></p><h3 style=\"letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><b>📦 Online / UPS</b></h3><p style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span class=\"s1\"></span></p><ul style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><li><p class=\"p1\">🏷️ Pack + label all orders correctly</p></li><li><p class=\"p1\">🚚 Make sure everything is dropped on time</p></li></ul><p style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"></p><p class=\"p2\" style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><br></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span class=\"s1\"></span></p><h3 style=\"letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><b>🛍️ Store Flow</b></h3><p style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span class=\"s1\"></span></p><ul style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><li><p class=\"p1\">🪞 Keep returns &amp; fitting rooms clean</p></li><li><p class=\"p1\">🧼 Don’t let things pile up</p></li><li><p class=\"p1\">👀 If something looks off, call it out</p></li></ul>",
